-- Marfin Bank in Talks With Russian, Chinese Investors, CyBC Says
-- B y   S t e l i o s   O r p h a n i d e s
-- 2012-02-24T05:41:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-24/marfin-bank-in-talks-with-russian-chinese-investors-cybc-says.html
Marfin Popular Bank Plc, Cyprus’s
second largest lender, submitted a recapitalization plan to the
 Central Bank of Cyprus , CyBC reported citing Marfin’s chairman
Michael Sarris.  The bank has held talks in recent weeks with potential
investors in Russia and  China , who may help the lender cope with
losses from Greek bonds, the Nicosia-based state radio reported
today, citing Sarris.  -- Editor: Chris Peterson  To contact the reporter on this story:
